com.dkriesel.snipe.core - package com.dkriesel.snipe.core
Contains the two core classes of SNIPE - NeuralNetworkDescriptor, which you use to outline and create instances of Neural Networks, and the NeuralNetwork class itself; Both of those classes' documentations, and the package documentation as well contain fundamental information to get used to SNIPE.
com.dkriesel.snipe.examples - package com.dkriesel.snipe.examples
Some easy programming examples to get used to SNIPE.
com.dkriesel.snipe.neuronbehavior - package com.dkriesel.snipe.neuronbehavior
Contains several neuron behaviors, which are generalized activity functions, as well as an interface to implement customized ones.
com.dkriesel.snipe.training - package com.dkriesel.snipe.training
Contains a class where to put in the training data for your neural network and one that contains several error measurement methods.
com.dkriesel.snipe.util - package com.dkriesel.snipe.util
Contains some SNIPE utilities: A random number generator (which is not mine; see its class documentation for copyright information) and a class which generates DOT-Code of a neural net in order to visualize a neural net using GraphViz.

createSynapsesAllowed() - Method in class com.dkriesel.snipe.core.NeuralNetwork
Adds all allowed synapses to the network topology in an more efficient way than adding lots of single ones with the setSynapse() method, with expected computational effort O(ALLOWEDSYNAPSES).
createSynapsesFromLayerToLayer(int, int) - Method in class com.dkriesel.snipe.core.NeuralNetwork
Creates a synapse from every neuron in the source layer to every neuron in the target layer, which may be the same, with computational effort O(SYNAPSESTOCREATE * SYNAPSECREATIONCOST) (look in the setSynapse documentation to learn about the latter).
createSynapsesFromLayerToLayerWithProbability(int, int, double) - Method in class com.dkriesel.snipe.core.NeuralNetwork
Creates a synapse from every neuron in the source layer to every neuron in the target layer (which may be the same) -- but only with a given probability and with computational effort O(SYNAPSESTOCREATE * SYNAPSECREATIONCOST) (look in the setSynapse documentation to learn about the latter).
createUserShadow(String) - Method in class com.dkriesel.snipe.core.NeuralNetwork
Creates a user shadow that is automatically adapted if network topology changes in time O(log(NUMBEROFSHADOWS)+log(SYNAPSES)).
